{"tid":1855181,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"同樣武漢出身既梁天琦同鄧晞真係好強烈對比","createTime":"2020-02-01T03:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T17:47:13.000Z","uid":104804,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60680dfd2404757cf181cfd588eacc9836b87470","tid":1855181,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"梁本土成長大學生熱愛香港坐監受苦<br />\n無社會地位無錢為香港人服務<br />\n<br />\n鄧海外精英愛國愛黨自私自利<br />\n哈佛清華受高等教育社會精英<br />\n係香港年薪上千萬高職位有社會地位<br />\n不過支性難改<br />\n玩弄香港人到處播毒不合作<br />\n仲要微信繼續扮慘呃人"},{"pid":"ac2c50b59ce6ceac95dca3c8a2e6eed6f7899d05","tid":1855181,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"天琦自細接受香港教育點同"},{"pid":"7052bd682d913b6b26f92800eac07d9a5a1c5035","tid":1855181,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天琦自細接受香港教育點同</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de730f7db1cf558560d188f7c2aab56b4d46b34","tid":1855181,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac2c50b59ce6ceac95dca3c8a2e6eed6f7899d05","tid":1855181,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"天琦自細接受香港教育點同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n<br />\n你喺上面讀書全部嘅書都係審查過甚至係共產黨自己寫嘅<br />\n<br />\n能夠唔愛黨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34947cd5ae8dfefbe8e17940355329ea4a2ed141","tid":1855181,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d8909b0aaccdd491f051e95de71bb9de85452ec","tid":1855181,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天琦自細接受香港教育點同</blockquote>咪就係<br />\n<br />\n你喺上面讀書全部嘅書都係審查過甚至係共產黨自己寫嘅<br />\n<br />\n能夠唔愛黨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁天琦的父親是教授中國歷史、漢語及佛學的中學老師[7]，喜歡研究清朝晚年、中華民國大陸時期、國民革命軍北伐、中國抗日戰爭、國共內戰等近代歷史[1][2]。母親在移居香港後從事家庭主婦[1]，後來擔任補習教師[7]。父親經常和梁天琦講述香港歷史和世界歷史，母親則教導他讀書識字[8]。梁天琦曾表示父親反對中國共產黨，母親則對中國共產黨有所恐懼[2]。其父親曾向《大公報》提到，自己對於中國大陸的制度並不滿意，但沒有不喜歡中國[4]。<br />\n<br />\nwiki"},{"pid":"816266016ca195caeec4182d497956dd270c7b1b","tid":1855181,"uid":277743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"唔知天琦係入面睇到d 新聞點呢。。"},{"pid":"e2134c8a81fc321850f0849b8f77015c4ab23d5a","tid":1855181,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de730f7db1cf558560d188f7c2aab56b4d46b34","tid":1855181,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac2c50b59ce6ceac95dca3c8a2e6eed6f7899d05","tid":1855181,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"天琦自細接受香港教育點同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n<br />\n你喺上面讀書全部嘅書都係審查過甚至係共產黨自己寫嘅<br />\n<br />\n能夠唔愛黨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:47:13.000Z","msg":"係香港金融界都叫有d地位<br />\n估唔到為人咁陰險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共產黨教出咁既垃圾"}]}